OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FRather cold and unsettled Thursday
OL,7,Fwith scattered heavy showers, chance
OL,8,Fof overnight frost. Mostly dry on
OL,9,FFriday with sunny spells. Dry, bright
OL,10,Fstart Saturday, chance of rain from
OL,11,Fwest later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
